971
01:14:01,687 --> 01:14:05,691
Saya wakil perundangan Syarikat Babel.

972
01:14:05,774 --> 01:14:08,026
Peguam Choi Myung-hee
dari Firma Guaman Wusang.

973
01:14:09,111 --> 01:14:13,240
